7357 /******************************************************************************/
7358 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F1xx device product */
7359 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
7360 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
7361 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
7362 /* product lines within the same STM32F1 Family */
